    <section name="Differential analysis">

      <p>This module allow to perform differntial analysis on expression module results.</p>  

      <ul>
         <li><b>Available</b>: Only in local mode.</li>
         <li><b>Optional parameters</b>: none.</li>

        <li><b>Usage</b>:
<source>
$ eoulsan.sh [options] anadiff design.txt
</source>

</li>
        
       </ul>
      
    </section>
    
    <section name="Required R packages installation">
    
    <p>Eoulsan differential analysis module use R as statistical backend. 
    Anadiff module was tested with R 2.10. You also need to install 2 R packages:</p>
    
    <ul>
        <li><b>statmod</b></li>
        <source>
$ wget http://cran.r-project.org/src/contrib/statmod_1.4.6.tar.gz
$ sudo R CMD INSTALL statmod_1.4.6.tar.gz
        </source>
        
        <li><b>edgeR</b></li>
        <source>
$ sudo R
&gt; source("http://bioconductor.org/biocLite.R")
&gt; biocLite("edgeR")       
        </source>
    </ul>
    
    
    
    </section>


